### PHASE 4 — Instant Work (InstantWork.jsx)

**Current**: List of countdown tasks
**Target**: Live countdown ticker cards — like a delivery tracking app

**Layout:**
```
┌─────────────────────────────┐
│ Instant Work           [New]│  ← Nav bar
├─────────────────────────────┤
│ [My Tasks] [Team] [History] │  ← Segmented control
